                "description": {
                    "value": "<p>The pitborn cavalry commands his mount to Stride twice directly toward a creature. The creature must attempt a @Check[will|dc:27] save. Regardless of the results of the save, the pitborn cavalry makes an axe Strike at the creature.</p><hr /><p><strong>Success</strong> The creature is unaffected.</p>\n<p><strong>Failure</strong> The creature is @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Frightened]{Frightened 1} and @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Off-Guard] to the giant until the start of the giant's next turn.</p>\n<p><strong>Critical Failure</strong> The creature is @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Frightened]{Frightened 2} for 1 minute and off-guard to the giant until the start of the giant's next turn.</p>"
